===Verb===
'''[[cop]] [[out]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[avoid]] or [[shirk]], either by failing to perform, or by performing in a grossly insufficient, negligent, or superficial manner.
#:''Faced with the prospect of cooking for himself, his first thought was to '''cop out''' and order a pizza.''

